29/10/2007
BUCHAREST, Romania -- NATO Secretary-General Jaap de Hoop Scheffer makes an official visit Monday (October 29th), laying the groundwork for April's Alliance summit in Bucharest. He will be meeting with President Traian Basescu, Prime Minister Calin Popescu Tariceanu, Foreign Minister Adrian Cioroianu, and senior interior and defence ministry officials. (Rompres, Nine o'clock - 29/10/07)
